<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>交互作用 Interaction</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/desc.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- head -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-left" onclick="location.href='/home'">
                <span class="welcome">交互作用</span>
                <span class="logo">Interaction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="header-right">
                <div class="header-right-contain">教學步驟<span>：前置準備</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="header-background"></div>
        <!-- head END-->
        <div class="main-background">
            前置準備：
            <br>
            <br>
            1.具備<span>麥克風</span>的電腦或<span>外接耳機麥克風</span>、<span>網路攝影機</span>。
            <br>
            2.安裝<span>&nbsp;OBS&nbsp;</span>串流軟體。
            <br>
            <br>
            <img src="img/steps.png">
            <br>
            <br>
            <br>
            <br>
            <div>OBS步驟：</div>
            <br>
            <img src="img/desc.png">
            <div class="main-contain-background">
                <div class="main-contain">
                    <br>
                    1.使用 OBS (Open Broadcaster Software) 進行直播。
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    2.打開 OBS > <span>設定</span>後，選擇左側的串流選項。
                </div>
                <div class="main-contain">
                    <br>
                    3.從<span>服務</span>的下拉列表中選擇<span>自訂</span>。
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    4.將以下<span>伺服器網址</span>以及<span>串流金鑰</span>，複製到 OBS 中<sapn>伺服器</sapn>、<span>串流金鑰</span>框中後點擊<span>套用</span>。
                </div>
                <div class="main-contain">
                    <br>
                    5.最後按下<span>開始串流</span>，於是就進行串流直播了。
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    6.回到網頁。
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
